2. The 11th day of August 2020 is appointed as the day on which the 
Credit Guarantee (Amendment) Act 2020 (No. 5 of 2020) shall come into 
operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

11 August, 2020. 

LEO VARADKAR, 

Minister for Business, Enterprise and Innovation. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 14th August, 2020.
